From 82c28e37d0c688d62ebe9f2d5b78145bdb7ffd9d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jack Thomson <jackabt@amazon.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 10:08:57 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 7/8] KVM: x86: Add KVM_CAP_ASYNC_PF_USERFAULT capability

Add KVM_CAP_ASYNC_PF_USERFAULT so userspace can discover support for
userfaultfd-based async page fault ioctl (KVM_ASYNC_PF with ops
KVM_APF_OP_READY, KVM_APF_OP_ACCEPT, KVM_APF_OP_SYNC_COMPLETE) and
the exitless eventfd notification mechanism (KVM_SET_APF_EVENTFD).

Signed-off-by: Jack Thomson <jackabt@amazon.com>
